 I:\prod\limits_{i=1}^n\hom(V_i,W)\to\hom\left(\bigoplus\limits_{i=1}^n V_i,W\right),\prod\limits_{i=1}^n f_i\mapsto\left(\bigoplus\limits_{i=1}^n v_i\mapsto\sum\limits_{i=1}^n f_i(v_i)\right) 
